{"tid":302002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又一隻 港女財困為2萬運毒往台灣被補","createTime":"2017-06-29T05:05:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-29T10:47:07.000Z","uid":72009,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8eceffc9a6d12e287a3ed3a47dd0450cea72470a","tid":302002,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T05:05:09.000Z","msg":"台灣航警局昨日破獲歷來最大宗的可卡因走私案，一名香港女子企圖攜帶8公斤可卡因入境台灣，在桃園機楊被查獲。<br />\n<br />\n航警局表示，該名27歲李姓女子昨日乘坐阿聯酋航空由杜拜飛往台北，由於台灣警方事前已接獲相關情報，安檢人員在李女所乘的航班抵台後立即展開跟監，結果在李女的行李中搜出數量高達8.05公斤的可卡因，估計市值近1億元新台幣（約2600萬港元），是航警局歷來破獲的最大宗可卡因走私案。<br />\n<br />\n李女偵訊時承認，由於失業缺錢，於是受託以2萬港元代價，將一批從巴西取得的可卡因帶到台灣，入境後再交給販毒集團成員。李女接受調查後，依違反毒品防制條例移送桃園地檢署偵辦，警方同時追查其他涉案人。&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170629/photo/bkn-20170629121013658-0629_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170629124821\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170629%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170629121013658-0629_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170629124821&h=60bdfd44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170629/mobile/bkn-20170629121013658-0629_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170629%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20170629121013658-0629_00822_001.html&d=oER3DYiZ3pJIOgB8YS%2FshEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=a5a75f44\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170629/mobile/bkn-20170629121013658-0629_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n台灣坐幾耐？"},{"pid":"fed749fc67e004477d61b61a809cdae3bcb58b8e","tid":302002,"uid":17813,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T05:06:40.000Z","msg":"依家啲人真係on9㗎喎,無100萬都唔做啦"},{"pid":"457d74096c67fdc42337521caf847fbe84d53040","tid":302002,"uid":114175,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T05:09: